Read TCA models

fn.lst <- list.files("~/bio/code/mpip/dex-stim-human-array/output/data/integrative/cell_type_enrichment", 
                      pattern = "*.RDS", full.names = TRUE)

tca.mdl <- lapply(fn.lst[-23], readRDS)
tca.mu.df <- lapply(tca.mdl, function(mdl) mdl$mus_hat)
tca.mu.df <- do.call(rbind, tca.mu.df) # mean of each BCC type in each CpG

dim(tca.mu.df)
## [1] 740357     12
tca.pval.df <- lapply(tca.mdl, function(mdl) mdl$gammas_hat_pvals.joint)
tca.pval.df <- do.call(rbind, tca.pval.df) # mean of each BCC type in each CpG

dim(tca.pval.df)
## [1] 740357      7

tca.mu.df <- rbind(tca.opposite.mu.df,
                   tca.parallel.delta.mu.df,
                   tca.parallel.veh.dex.mu.df)

tca.mu.df[["CpG_ID"]] <- rownames(tca.mu.df)

melt.df   <- tca.mu.df %>% reshape2::melt(id.vars = c("CpG_ID", "Model")) 

ggplot(melt.df, aes(y = value, x = Model, fill = variable)) +
  geom_boxplot() +
  scale_fill_viridis(discrete = TRUE, alpha = 0.3, option = "C") +
  labs(title = " ", y = "Mean estimates", x = " ") + 
  facet_wrap(~ variable, ncol = 6, nrow = 2) +
  theme(legend.position = "none", 
        legend.title = element_blank(),
        panel.grid.major = element_blank(),
        panel.background = element_blank(),
        plot.title = element_text(size = 10),
        axis.title = element_text(size = 8),
        axis.title.x = element_blank(),
        axis.text.x = element_text(angle = 25, hjust = 0.5))

Box-plots showing distribution of estimates for the mean of each blood cell type in each CpG
